Constructor for RawDataset object

raw_dataset.Rd

raw_dataset(x)

Arguments

x

(data.frame or rtable) object

Examples

library(random.cdisc.data)
ADSL <- radsl(cached = TRUE)
ADSL_dataset <- raw_dataset(x = ADSL)

ADSL_dataset$get_raw_data()
